{
  "stem": "766.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the day when they were supposed to come, she put them between two walls in the wall to hide them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Meanwhile, they took them away, the parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And later, all the houses were from wood was the slums.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "These people steal, removed everything for a little heat, found two skeletons, the two children which she put over there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She thought that they will save the children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nobody knew that over there are two children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This was such shocks and to live here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember when there were the big [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They took my mother to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I had another--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Appel and we had to be downstairs in the back yard-- if there wasn't, the street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some were hiding here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Than they found them right away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother, we were honest to say-- go down, it's down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took her under then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was in the shock.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So a colleague of mine went over to a German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somehow, he had luck with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, you know, this woman is the mother of her doctor and maybe you let her go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he says, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I saved my mother until the end when the ghetto was liquidated, until we went to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But this is the-- now, during the times of the ghetto, start coming transports from abroad, which always at night so we shouldn't see it probably.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the morning, we found out new people from Berlin, from Czechoslovakia, from Prague, a boss of my brother's where when he was in Prague, he didn't have the right to work.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But probably he tried to help him to do something-- happened to be a Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he came with two daughters.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
